EQUIPMENT: Show currently equipped items and tattoos

Syntax: equipment
        eq

DESCRIPTION:
  Displays all items you have equipped on your body, by slot, along with
  any active Atlantean tattoos.

OUTPUT FORMAT:
  Right hand:  <weapon or empty>
  Left hand:   <weapon or empty>
  <slot>:      <armor piece or shield>
  ...
  Tattoos:     <tattoo name> (<location>), ...

NOTES:
  Tattoo weapons (flaming sword, spear, dagger) appear in the weapon
  slots once summoned and wielded.

  Temporary tattoo effects (armor fields, power effects) are not shown
  in the equipment list but can be seen in your score or status.

SEE ALSO: touch, score, wield, wear, remove
